Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare tu abbia bevuto molta acqua, Shiraki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Te ne farò bere molta anche da qui sotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Fermati!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Non esiti a bere molto, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fà male...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fà male!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, fermati!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi esploderà lo stomaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Devi farci divertire di più.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Non ti impegni abbastanza, Shiraki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ora dimmi Shiraki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosa stavi curiosando in giro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:01.79,Note,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ospedale Generale{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:15.14,Note,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lchikawa Aki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,La Lancia di Longino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:30.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ospedale Generale{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Che incubo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Visto che non posso prenderti la verginità, penso che mi accomoderò con questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fà male!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,E' caldo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sta entrando!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,La Lancia di Longino...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, è bella fresca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,E' inutile resistere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammi la Lancia di Longino...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stai bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve un dottore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma che diavolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,E' imbarazzante.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lo voglio anche io, Jody-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo. Continua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Da adesso, sarai i miei occhi ed orecchie. Ora sei la mia fedele servitrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, Jody-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Voglio che me lo dia, Jody-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Promettimelo, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, lo prometto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarò la sua fedele servitrice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,E prometto di aiutarvi a realizzare la profezia del grande Aleister Crowley-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Meraviglioso...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jody-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, sì, Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sto godendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:22.86,Note,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dimissioni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sta respingendo il mio rapporto come una sciocchezza e mi sta togliendo il caso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Non ho altra scelta che dimettermi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Molte grazie per tutto, addio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosa pensi di  fare dopo questo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuerò ad indagare su questo caso da solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Capisco...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma sarà difficile non avendo un'organizzazione ad aiutarti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sopratutto in un caso come questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Voglio davvero risolvere questo caso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,L'indirizzo dell'agenzia indagini speciali, Tokken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Vedi, il capo della Tokken si chiama Yuge Toru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ci conosciamo sin dai tempi dell'accademia di polizia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Disse la stessa cosa che hai detto tu e lasciò questo posto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Puoi restare in questa stanza finché non tornerà Imari-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, la ringrazio molto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho lasciato la documentazione sulla scrivania.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fammi sapere cosa ne pensi dopo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, signore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, e smettila di salutarmi in quel modo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Non siamo ufficiali di polizia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Viene dalla mia scuola?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Era iscritta come studente lo stesso anno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Quando Kitami-sensei si trasferì in un altra scuola...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei? Si sta trasferendo in un'altra scuola?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Non potrò più vederti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Non voglio che se ne vada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamanishi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Voglio che tu mi dia dei bei ricordi di questa scuola.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Davvero le piaccio anche io?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Non fare domande.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,E' la mia prima volta perciò...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Va bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sii gentile con me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,E' bello...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono felice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Continua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sii gentile con me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,E' imbarazzante...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...ma sono felice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lasciami farlo a te ora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, non fissarmi così.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,E' bellissimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fà male?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sta bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, sto bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma tu ti senti a tuo agio?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì, mi sento alla grande...Kitami-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiamami Reika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Va bene...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, posso cominciare a muovermi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sì.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.97,0:24:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono tornata.
